name: test
query:
SELECT 
    item_code,
CONCAT(posting_date, ' ', posting_time) AS 'date_time',
posting_date,
posting_time,
    warehouse,
    SUM(CASE WHEN actual_qty >= 0 THEN actual_qty ELSE 0 END) AS 'Actual_In_Qty',
    SUM(CASE WHEN actual_qty < 0 THEN -actual_qty ELSE 0 END) AS 'Actual_Out_Qty',
    SUM(qty_after_transaction) AS 'Actual_Balance_Qty',
    SUM(CASE WHEN custom_nosquantity >= 0 THEN custom_nosquantity ELSE 0 END) AS 'Custom_In_Qty',
    SUM(CASE WHEN custom_nosquantity < 0 THEN -custom_nosquantity ELSE 0 END) AS 'Custom_Out_Qty',
    SUM(custom_nosquantity_after_transaction) AS 'Custom_Balance_Qty',
    batch_no,
    serial_no,
    voucher_type
FROM `tabStock Ledger Entry`
GROUP BY 
    Voucher_Detail_No,
    item_code,
    date_time,
    warehouse,
    batch_no,
    serial_no
